{"tid":979322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黏手、有怪味！黑心商家用垃圾污水製作醃肉","createTime":"2019-01-12T15:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T15:32:03.000Z","uid":51183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2afac60444bcfad4fa6316dc60ef56984db576ca","tid":979322,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/536718613512319/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F536718613512319%2F&d=CY9p5aGPUbqKbEJsZLRVzozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=270700d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/536718613512319/</a><br />\n<br />\n有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n【黏手、有怪味！】<br />\n【黑心商家用垃圾污水製作醃肉】<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體近日揭發江蘇南京一個工場違規生產醃肉，幾百呎的房間污漬斑斑，加工用的豬腳堆滿在地上。<br />\n<br />\n接著，工人將凍肉放入這個傳出陣陣惡臭的黑色污水池浸泡，水面漂浮著泡沫和塑膠，水底全部都是豬腳。<br />\n<br />\n工場內連一個水龍頭都沒有，他們用的，就是這些布滿垃圾、且駁到廁所的坑渠水。<br />\n<br />\n這些腌肉會送到鄰近「李飛食品店」出售，雖然醃肉聞上去有怪味，但店主稱每日都會批發賣出幾千斤。現時工場同舖頭都已被取締。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12ade0bdf931c9ba90d2f6c9beba678c4103325","tid":979322,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"污水配豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}